<p style="text-align: right;">!!!מזל טוב לסיירים החדשים</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/NewRangersMay29.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4609" title="NewRangersMay29" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/NewRangersMay29.png" alt="" width="447" height="379" /></a></p>
